flowchart TD
  Story[The story in your head] --> Q1{Is it actually\ntrue?}
  Q1 -->|no| Drop[Drop it]
  Q1 -->|yes| Q2{Is it the whole\npicture?}
  Q2 -->|no| Expand[Add the missing facts]
  Q2 -->|yes| Q3{Is it useful\nto hold right now?}
  Q3 -->|no| Park[Park it]
  Q3 -->|yes| Keep[Use it]
  Expand --> Q3
